h care services through practitioners licensed by the State of Hawaii, where licensure requirements are applicable,","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11711/6/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11711/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs11711%2F6%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"which is a public or nonprofit private entity,","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11711/6/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11711/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs11711%2F6%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"in which Native Hawaiian health practitioners significantly participate in the planning, management, monitoring, and evaluation of health care services,","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"E","heading":null,"label":"E","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11711/6/E","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11711/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs11711%2F6%2FE","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"which may be composed of as many Native Hawaiian health centers as necessary to meet the health care needs of each island’s Native Hawaiians, and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"F","heading":null,"label":"F","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11711/6/F","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t42/s11711/6","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft42%2Fs11711%2F6%2FF","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","nu